title: Improved comments
message:
Improved comments
Minor change following warning (API version for getTextContent()) produced by new ADT
other minor project properties and classpath file changes caused by new ADT

title: Added support for locating BLOBbox IP via UPnP SSDP
message:
Added support for locating BLOBbox IP via UPnP SSDP 
- if no IP specified at Configure time, scan for boxes and use first IP found
- display what is blobbox only if no boxes found.

title: Moved debug TAG into Constants
message:
Moved debug TAG into Constants
Added version name to info text
Moved playback title and info strings into strings.xml
Updated version to 1.0.2

title: Refactored Handlers to move common code into AbstractArgoOperationHandler.
message:
Refactored Handlers to move common code into AbstractArgoOperationHandler.
Moved constants into a final class (avoid interface for constants)

title: Improved error handling - needs refactoring to move duplicate code fromâ€¦
message: Improved error handling - needs refactoring to move duplicate code from Configure and AbstractBLOBboxActivity into a common class

title: Followed instructions from link below to allow app relocation to SD card
message:
Followed instructions from link below to allow app relocation to SD card
  http://developer.android.com/guide/appendix/install-location.html

title: Moved registering of preference change listener from onCreate to onResume.
message:
Moved registering of preference change listener from onCreate to onResume.
Added de-registration of such listener in onPause.
